summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, amending Plat 221E, page 8 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone the property located at approximately 13000 Lake City Way Northeast from Lowrise 2 (L-2) to Commercial 1 with a 40-foot height limit (C1/40'). (Petition of Fred Meyer, Inc., C.F. 299398)
committee: Housing, Community Development and Urban Environment
